
Download & install VirtualBox
Download Ubuntu image
Import the Ubuntu image to the VirtualBox and configure the network
  NAT [Network Address Translation] (default mode): use the host ip
                      virtual machine -> host
                      virtual machine -> external internet (if host can access the external internet)
                      DHCP -> virtual machine IP
  NAT Network: plus function based on NAT
               virtual machine <-> virtual machine
               vritual machine <- host (if port forwarding is configured)
